      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">

          <identifier>

          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Baseball Cards, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Baseballkarten, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cartes de Base-ball, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Cartões De Baseball, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Schedi Di Baseball, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κάρτες μπέιζ-μπώλ, 1887-1914</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Tarjetas De Béisbol, 1887-1914</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">presents 2,100 early baseball cards. The cards show such legendary figures as Ty Cobb stealing third base, Tris Speaker batting, and pitcher Cy Young formally posing. Other notable players include Connie Mack, Walter Johnson, King Kelly, and Christy Mathematics and Statisticsewson.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Geschenke 2.100 frühe Baseballkarten. Die 
Karten zeigen solche legendäre Abbildungen, die Ty Cobb, das dritte 
Unterseite, Tris Sprecherschlagen und die formal aufwerfenden Krug Cy 
Junge stiehlt. Andere bemerkenswerte Spieler enthalten Connie 
Mack, Walter Johnson, König Kelly und Christy Mathematik und 
Statisticsewson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">présents 2.100 cartes de base-ball tôt. 
Les cartes montrent de telles figures légendaires comme Ty Cobb
volant la troisième base, ouate en feuille d'orateur de Tris, et 
jeunes de Cy de pichet posant formellement. D'autres joueurs 
notables incluent Connie Mack, Walter Johnson, Roi Kelly, et 
mathématiques et Statisticsewson de Christy.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">presentes 2.100 cartões de baseball adiantados. 
Os cartões mostram tais figuras legendárias como Ty Cobb que 
rouba a terceiros base, batedura do altofalante de Tris, e jovens de 
Cy do jarro que posing formalmente. Outros jogadores notáveis 
incluem Connie Mack, Walter Johnson, rei Kelly, e matemática e 
Statisticsewson de Christy.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">presenti 2.100 schedi di baseball in anticipo. 
Le schedi mostrano tali figure leggendarie come Ty Cobb che ruba
terzi base, ovatta dell'altoparlante di Tris e giovani di Cy del 
lanciatore che propongono formalmente. Altri giocatori notevoli
includono Connie Mack, Walter Johnson, re Kelly e la matematica e 
Statisticsewson di Christy.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">παρουσιάζει 2.100 πρόωρες κάρτες μπέιζ-μπώλ. 
Οι κάρτες εμφανίζουν τέτοιους θρυλικούς αριθμούς όπως 
Ty Cobb κλέβοντας την τρίτη βάση, να κτυπήσουν ομιλητών 
Tris, και νεολαίες της Κύπρου σταμνών που θέτουν τυπικά. 
Αλλοι ξεχωριστοί φορείς περιλαμβάνουν Connie Mack, 
walter Johnson, kelly βασιλιάδων, και μαθηματικά Christy
και Statisticsewson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">presentes 2.100 tarjetas de béisbol tempranas. 
Las tarjetas muestran las figuras legendarias tales que Ty Cobb 
que roba la tercera base, batting del locutor de Tris, y jóvenes de 
Cy de la jarra que se presentan formalmente. Otros jugadores 
notables incluyen Connie Mack, Walter Johnson, rey Kelly, y las 
matemáticas y Statisticsewson de Christy.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
